{"title":"Từ vựng mỗi ngày (Day 3) Những từ ghép với 気","uid":"10d64f9af108d3082276ee726435f859","slug":"tuvungmoingay3","date":"2023-02-12T08:33:31.000Z","updated":"2023-02-13T13:40:29.677Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/tuvungmoingay3.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"気が〜\"><a href=\"#気が〜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"気が〜\"></a>気が〜</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">No</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Goi</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vocab</th>\n<th align=\"left\">English Meaning</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vietnamese Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が合う</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga au)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be compatible with</td>\n<td align=\"left\">khớp với nhau</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がある</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga aru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to have a feeling about something</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy một cái gì đó</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がいい</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ii)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel good about</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tốt tâm trạng về một cái gì đó</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が多い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ooi)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be overly sensitive</td>\n<td align=\"left\">quá nhạy cảm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が大きい</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ooki)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be conceited</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tự cao</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が置けない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga okenai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be unable to put aside one’s feeling</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không thể xóa bỏ cảm xúc của mình</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が重い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga omoi)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel heavy or burdened</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy nặng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が勝つ</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga katsu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to have a strong will</td>\n<td align=\"left\">có lòng muốn mạnh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が利く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga kiku)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be sharp or clever</td>\n<td align=\"left\">sắc sảo hoặc thông minh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が腐る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga kusaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to become disillusioned</td>\n<td align=\"left\">trở nên hoang tưởng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">11</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が差す</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga sasu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be affected by something</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị ảnh hưởng bởi một cái gì đó</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">12</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が知れない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga shirenai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be unknown</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không biết</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">13</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が進まない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga susumanai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be unmotivated</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không có động lực</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">14</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が済む</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga sumu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel relieved</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy giải tỏa</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">15</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がする</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga suru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to have a feeling or intuition</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy hoặc tinh tấu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">16</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が急く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga isogu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be impatient</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không cần thiết</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が合う</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga au)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be compatible with</td>\n<td align=\"left\">khớp với nhau</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がある</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga aru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be in the mood</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm xúc tốt</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がいい</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ii)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be in a good mood</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm xúc tốt</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が多い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ooi)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be abundant</td>\n<td align=\"left\">nhiều</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が大きい</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga ookii)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be large, imposing</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to lớn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が置けない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga okenai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be restless</td>\n<td align=\"left\">mệt mỏi</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が重い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga omoi)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be heavy</td>\n<td align=\"left\">nặng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が勝つ</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga katsu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to win the battle of nerves</td>\n<td align=\"left\">thắng trận cảm xúc</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が利く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga kiku)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be effective</td>\n<td align=\"left\">hiệu quả</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が腐る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga kusaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to become discouraged</td>\n<td align=\"left\">từ bỏ</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">11</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が差す</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga sasu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be discouraged</td>\n<td align=\"left\">suy nghĩ tồi tệ</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">12</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が知れない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga shirenai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be unpredictable</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không dự đoán được</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">13</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が進まない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga susumanai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be discouraged</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không cảm hứng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が済む</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga sumu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be settled</td>\n<td align=\"left\">đã giải quyết</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がする</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga suru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が急く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga isogu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be impatient</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bất cẩn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がそがれる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga sogareru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be discouraged</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị thất vọng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が立つ</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga tatsu)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to get angry</td>\n<td align=\"left\">giận dữ</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が小さい</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga chiisai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be petty</td>\n<td align=\"left\">nhỏ nhặt</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が散る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga chiru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be scattered</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị rải rác</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が尽きる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga tsukiru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be exhausted</td>\n<td align=\"left\">mệt mỏi</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が詰まる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga tsumaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be stuffy</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cứng cỏi</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が遠くなる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga tooku naru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel distant</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy xa lạ</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">11</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が咎める</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga togamemoru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to blame</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tố cáo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">12</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が無い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga nai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to not care</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không quan tâm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">13</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が長い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga nagai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be patient</td>\n<td align=\"left\">kiên nhẫn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">14</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が抜ける</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga nukeru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel relieved</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy giải tỏa</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">15</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が乗る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga noru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be in the mood</td>\n<td align=\"left\">trong tâm trạng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">16</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が早い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga hayai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be fast</td>\n<td align=\"left\">nhanh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">17</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が張る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga haru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be tense</td>\n<td align=\"left\">căng thẳng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">18</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が晴れる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga hareru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to feel better</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cảm thấy tốt hơn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">19</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が引ける</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga hikeru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be disappointed</td>\n<td align=\"left\">thất vọng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気がふれる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga fureru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be affected by</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị ảnh hưởng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が減る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga heru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to decrease</td>\n<td align=\"left\">giảm xuống</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が紛れる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga magireru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be diverted</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị lạc</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が回る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga mawaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to turn</td>\n<td align=\"left\">xoay</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が短い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga mijikai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be short-tempered</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tính tức ngắn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が向く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga muku)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to incline</td>\n<td align=\"left\">định hướng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が揉める</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga momeru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be disturbed</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị gây rối</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気が若い</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ga wakai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be youthful</td>\n<td align=\"left\">có tính trẻ trung</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"気を〜\"><a href=\"#気を〜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"気を〜\"></a>気を〜</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">No</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Goi</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vocab</th>\n<th align=\"left\">English Meaning</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vietnamese Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を入れる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to put effort into</td>\n<td align=\"left\">chăm chỉ vào</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を失う</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to lose focus</td>\n<td align=\"left\">mất tập trung</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を落とす</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to let one’s guard down</td>\n<td align=\"left\">nhảy nhịp</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を兼ねる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be careful and considerate</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cẩn thận và thân thiện</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を利かせる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to use one’s influence</td>\n<td align=\"left\">sử dụng sức ảnh hưởng của mình</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を砕く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to break one’s spirit</td>\n<td align=\"left\">phá vỡ niềm tin của ai</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を遣う</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be concerned about</td>\n<td align=\"left\">quan tâm đến</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を尽くす</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to put in maximum effort</td>\n<td align=\"left\">đầu tư sức lực tối đa</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を付け</td>\n<td align=\"left\">be careful</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cẩn thận</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を取り直す</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to get back one’s spirit</td>\n<td align=\"left\">lấy lại niềm tin</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">11</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を抜く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to loosen up</td>\n<td align=\"left\">giải tỏa</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">12</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を呑まれる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be absorbed in</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị hấp hối vào</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">13</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を吐く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to vent one’s anger</td>\n<td align=\"left\">thổi phồng giận dữ</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">14</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を張る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be nervous</td>\n<td align=\"left\">căng thẳng</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">15</td>\n<td align=\"left\">油を引く</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to pull back</td>\n<td align=\"left\">rút lại</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">16</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を回す</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to recover</td>\n<td align=\"left\">khỏi phục</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">17</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を持たせる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to keep one’s spirit up</td>\n<td align=\"left\">giữ niềm tin</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">18</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を揉む</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to worry</td>\n<td align=\"left\">lo lắng</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">19</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を許す</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to forgive</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tha thứ</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">20</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気を良くする</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to brighten one’s mood</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tạo niềm vui</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"他の\"><a href=\"#他の\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"他の\"></a>他の</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">No</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Goi</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vocab</th>\n<th align=\"left\">English Meaning</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Vietnamese Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気に掛かる</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ni kakaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to worry about</td>\n<td align=\"left\">lo lắng về</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気に掛ける</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ni kakeru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to pay attention to</td>\n<td align=\"left\">chú ý đến</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気に食わない</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ni kuwanai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">not to like</td>\n<td align=\"left\">không thích</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気に障る</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki ni sawaru)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">to be bothered by</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bị làm phiền</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気の所為</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki no sei)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">because of one’s mood</td>\n<td align=\"left\">vì tâm trạng của một người</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気の病</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki no yamai)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">mood swing</td>\n<td align=\"left\">sự thay đổi tâm trạng</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\">気は心</td>\n<td align=\"left\">(ki wa kokoro)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">spirit is heart</td>\n<td align=\"left\">tâm trạng là trái tim</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n","feature":true,"text":"気が〜 No Goi Vocab English Meaning Vietnamese Meaning 1 気が合う (ki ga au) to be compatible with khớp với nhau 2 気がある (ki ga aru) to have a feeli...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.6k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Japanese","slug":"Japanese","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Japanese.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"DailyJapanese","slug":"DailyJapanese","count":3,"path":"api/tags/DailyJapanese.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B0%97%E3%81%8C%E3%80%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">気が〜</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B0%97%E3%82%92%E3%80%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">気を〜</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%96%E3%81%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">他の</span></a></li></ol>","